name: Warm Rabbit
description:
When I was a child my family used to tell me stories about a distant relative of us, who lived in a house with a huge field.
Apparently he kept animal skulls on a shelf in his living room. He always said that he found the animals already dead, but no one really believed that.
I've always remembered this stories fearing that this animals would take revange on us, on his family (too many horror movies maybe)

Part of the "Luz Mala" collection
